{"tid":963344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得未來十年將會係日本既黃金時代?","createTime":"2018-12-31T13:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T22:41:54.000Z","uid":39181,"like":13,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6019b6f551f4f6acdedb5844f4bf0f05c4c33a","tid":963344,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:40:23.000Z","msg":"雖然日本依家都好勁，但可以再創高峰 <br />\n2019年開始日本將會開新時代，之後又有搞萬博、奧運，一定會產生新既景氣，仲韜光養晦咗咁耐，一定積存咗好多實力，日本風亦可能再次興起，好似以前咁潮流跟日本，香港變番個個留長頭髮既時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港女亦變得好日系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正所謂風水輪流轉，08年至依家係中國既興盛時期係畀佢問鼎霸者既機會，但都仍未成功挑戰到美國，係時候要畀下一位競爭者去挑戰，而中國就返去迷失下十年好好反省自己既失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c534a4806e2e72b0ea7c35ec5c462a0211a8912","tid":963344,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"一定係我地中國之後韓國 再一齊帶紅返日本"},{"pid":"da0265f68a47feb98cf4217ddc7c3fb2041dbc9c","tid":963344,"uid":38904,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:45:32.000Z","msg":"1. 人口老化<br />\n2. 通縮<br />\n搞掂咗先好講黃金時代"},{"pid":"fb605ca08cabc3043d8ffa21e1ce9ae8889c26a7","tid":963344,"uid":179409,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"da0265f68a47feb98cf4217ddc7c3fb2041dbc9c","tid":963344,"uid":38904,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:45:32.000Z","msg":"1. 人口老化<br />\n2. 通縮<br />\n搞掂咗先好講黃金時代"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"人口老化無得搞<br />\n咪話拍拖結婚生仔<br />\n日本後生一輩好多連真人都唔想接觸<br />\n反正上網可以滿足一切慾望<br />\n唔想煩咁多嘢"},{"pid":"b9c7e0dab9826f35e970669c410523fd55c60c90","tid":963344,"uid":3112,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fb605ca08cabc3043d8ffa21e1ce9ae8889c26a7","tid":963344,"uid":179409,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"da0265f68a47feb98cf4217ddc7c3fb2041dbc9c","tid":963344,"uid":38904,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy"